st to train with.  I'd like a Focused Ethereal Greatsword...while not great, it's wonderful for my level...so now I have to find someone hunting Skyshrine. <p><center><font size=+2><a href="http://pub66.ezboard.com/bmaidensfancy">Shiden Kaidan</a></font><br><font size=1><i><a href="http://www.neriak.com/">Tier'dal</a> <a href="http://interealms.com/shadowknight/">Knight</a></i></font> of the<a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/"> Firiona Vie</a> Server<br><font color=red>@}</font><font color=green>--,---'---</font><br><i>"Let nothing stand in the way of power."</i></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukallee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kallee</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dances with Skeletons</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/17/02 10:44:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=47.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Need 2hs weapons</span><hr size=1> Shiden,  I've been considering doing the Reaper quest, so if you want (I don't know what level you are...) maybe we can hook up and do that sometime.  <br>And if you supply materials, I can perhaps make for you a forged two hander to hold you over until you can get your hands on something better.<br>Look me up in game, or PM me...or email from the journal <br><br> <p>Kallee<BR>14th Rank Shadow Knight<BR><a href=http://www.geocities.com/ladymaya01/kalleejournal.html>Kallee's Journal</a><BR><i>My dream may be your nightmare</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umadrain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>madrain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kerran Lord</span><br>  Posts: 233<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/17/02 7:53:59 pm)</font><br>   <